# mutt-config

Based heavily on work by [Patrick Brisbin][1].

Accounts are included as a `git module` for privacy. See [an example][2] by
Patrick if necessary.

## Usage

Run:

    mkdir -p "$XDG_CACHE_HOME"/mutt/{headers,tmp}

    data="$XDG_DATA_HOME/mutt"
    mkdir -p "$data"
    touch "$data/aliases"

